#compdef mdbook-autosummary
# _mdbook-autosummary — auto-generate SUMMARY.md from folder structure (hypergonial/mdbook-autosummary)
# upstream: https://github.com/hypergonial/mdbook-autosummary
# Subcommands from src/main.rs (clap App).

_mdbook-autosummary() {
    _arguments \
        '1:command:(supports version)' \
        '2:renderer:(html epub markdown latex)'
}

_mdbook-autosummary "$@"
